data.description: Offering Columbus taxes in Westerville Schools, this two-story residence offers both quiet and convenience.  Step inside and be greeted by the spacious and light-filled living areas. The open floor plan connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a welcoming atmosphere for entertaining. In addition to the first floor owners suite with a walk-in closet and 3/4 bath, there are two upstairs bedrooms and a full bathroom. The location of the home in addition to the partially fenced back yard allows room for gatherings while also providing privacy. With easy access to nearby amenities, parks, shopping centers, and dining establishments, you'll have everything you need within reach. Roof replaced in 2022. HVAC maintained every year. Deck added in 2023.
